    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready for your dream ride? I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s in showroom condition! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one\u2014not a scratch or a dent anywhere. It still has that fresh smell and drives like it just rolled off the lot. You won\u2019t find another one this clean on the market. Come take a look, you\u2019re going to fall in love at first sight!",
