    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional E46 M3, a definitive analog masterpiece featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six. This specimen delivers 333hp through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. Critical preventative maintenance is complete: the VANOS system has been bulletproofed, rod bearings replaced with treated shells, and the rear subframe reinforced with plates. The chassis remains rigid, and the factory limited-slip differential provides optimal lock-up. Finished in pristine Alpine White over Nappa leather, the interior shows zero bolster wear. This is a turn-key, investment-grade example with a documented service history and flawless mechanical synchronization.",
