      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-standard vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This car has been kept in a climate-controlled garage since day one and has never seen rain, let alone snow. The exterior paint is flawless, protected by a multi-layer ceramic coating that provides a deep, liquid-like gloss. Inside, the interior is pristine; the upholstery shows no signs of wear, the bolsters are firm, and the original factory protective films are still present on several trim pieces. Mechanically, the car is perfect, with a full documented service history from the original dealership. It drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line\u2014tight, responsive, and powerful. This is not just a used car; it is a time capsule for the enthusiast who demands perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
