      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m parting with this absolute gem and it is seriously in pristine, showroom condition. It\u2019s been pampered in a garage, still has that fresh interior smell, and drives like an absolute dream! Not a single scratch or speck of dust to be found\u2014it\u2019s basically brand new. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and I just know you\u2019re going to be obsessed the moment you see it. Come grab this beauty before someone else does!",
