    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3 in pristine, unmodified condition. This example is powered by the S54B32 high-revving inline-six, featuring an 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual and a variable M differential lock. Critical preventative maintenance is fully documented, including a reinforced rear subframe, Beisan Systems VANOS overhaul, and rod bearing replacement. The suspension retains its factory-tuned kinematics with zero bushing play. The exterior finish is flawless, showing no signs of track use or environmental wear. A mechanically superior specimen for the discerning collector.",
